data.description: This newer home, built in 2020 is now available! The entryway leads into the main level which includes a living room, dining area, and kitchen. Upstairs you'll find three bedrooms located on the same level. Primary bedroom includes a walk in closet and private bath. Second 3/4 bath located on this level as well. Lower level has 709 finished square feet with walk out patio door to fenced in back yard. This level includes a third 3/4 bath as well as a laundry/ mud room. The four car garage has inside stairway access to the third level laundry/ mud room. The fourth level includes unfinished space and a lookout window. Only a job relocation makes this home available.
